    <item>
      <title>BMO 的戴维斯表示，贸易战可能引发通胀冲击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-03/trade-war-could-cause-inflation-shock-says-bmo-s-davis-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[BMO 全球资产管理公司固定收益和货币市场主管 Earl Davis 表示，与墨西哥和加拿大的贸易和关税战可能导致通胀冲击。他谈到了对全球债券市场的影响。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-03/trade-war-could-cause-inflation-shock-says-bmo-s-davis-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 16:34:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税将如何影响全球旅行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-03/how-tariffs-could-hit-global-travel-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普总统的关税可能会对全球旅游业产生深远影响。InteleTravel 联合创始人兼总裁 James Ferrara 参加了彭博公开交易，谈论了他对早期贸易战影响的看法。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-02-03/how-tariffs-could-hit-global-travel-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 16:25:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大股市下跌，因美国关税可能带来回调</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/canadian-stocks-could-see-major-correction-after-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普上周末签署关税行政命令后，加拿大基准股市出现自 8 月以来的最大跌幅，分析师表示，长期来看可能出现大幅回调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/canadian-stocks-could-see-major-correction-after-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 14:05:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰森食品利润猛增 为特朗普贸易战做好准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/tyson-raises-profit-outlook-as-chicken-drives-strong-results</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰森食品公司表示，由于关税威胁到其对墨西哥的猪肉出口，该公司正在努力应对唐纳德·特朗普发起的贸易战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/tyson-raises-profit-outlook-as-chicken-drives-strong-results</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 12:30:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税推迟，墨西哥比索兑美元大幅反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/mexican-peso-rand-lead-em-currency-selloff-on-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥比索领涨风险货币，而受美国对墨西哥征收关税将推迟一个月的消息影响，美元几乎抹去了涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/mexican-peso-rand-lead-em-currency-selloff-on-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 01:48:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券市场显示担忧关税将引发通胀和经济增长冲击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/treasuries-fall-on-short-end-as-tariffs-deepen-inflation-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国债券市场向总统唐纳德·特朗普发出警告，对主要贸易伙伴征收关税可能会加剧通胀并减缓美国经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/treasuries-fall-on-short-end-as-tariffs-deepen-inflation-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 01:14:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>基本金属抹去跌幅，因交易商权衡特朗普关税范围</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/iron-ore-drops-as-trump-tariffs-raise-global-growth-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于围绕特朗普总统对中国、加拿大和墨西哥征收关税的范围以及对全球经济增长的影响存在不确定性，从铜到铝等工业金属价格抹去了损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/iron-ore-drops-as-trump-tariffs-raise-global-growth-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 00:57:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税带来的经济冲击抵消了供应限制，油价出现波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-3</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普将对墨西哥征收关税的计划推迟了一个月，投资者评估了加征关税可能减缓全球经济增长的可能性，从而削弱了人们对短期供应限制的担忧，导致油价出现波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-3</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 23:03:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美墨关税希望升温，股市脱离低点：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/dollar-surges-stocks-set-to-fall-on-trump-tariffs-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普确认，他与墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·谢因鲍姆达成协议，立即暂停征收关税一个月，刺激比索快速反弹，随后股市从盘中低点回升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/dollar-surges-stocks-set-to-fall-on-trump-tariffs-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 22:25:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
